| ShortSummary        = Aihara is suffering from severe homesickness, which sends him over the edge when he contacts Earth and sees his father die before his very eyes.  After his appeals to Shima to turn the ship around fail, Aihara decides to strike out for home himself, not suspecting that he's being lured into a Gamilas trap.
}}
